#. type: multicols
#: sections/trading.tex:16
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Trading Post actions}\n"
"When visiting a \\pagelink{Trading Post}{Trading Post Field}, choose one:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Trade multiple Resources with the game in accordance with the \\hyperlink{Trade Table}{table at the back cover}.\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}[before skip balanced=0.4em,left=4mm]{rampart,cove}\n"
"    \\item Buy a \\pagelink{War Machines}{War Machine} of your choice.\n"
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Remove a single card} from your hand to gain 1 \\svg{gold}.\\par\n"
"    \\note{4}{Specialty, Statistic, Starting Ability and \\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{Magic Arrows} \\textbf{cannot be removed} in the Trading Post.}\\par\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{贸易站行动}\n"
"访问\\pagelink{Trading Post}{贸易站格}时，你可以选择：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item 按照\\hyperlink{Trade Table}{封底的表格}与游戏交易多种资源，或\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}[before skip balanced=0.4em,left=4mm]{rampart,cove}\n"
"    \\item 购买一台\\pagelink{War Machines}{战争机器}，或\n"
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"  \\item 在贸易站从你的手牌中\\textbf{移除一张牌}，以获得1\\svg{gold}。\n"
"    \\note{4}{特长、属性、初始能力和\\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{魔法箭}\\textbf{不能在贸易站被移除}。}\\par\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/trading.tex:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"In addition to the above, players can do following free actions an unlimited number of times during the same visit:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item In \\textbf{Cooperative Scenarios}: Resources may be given to other players.\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}[before skip balanced=0.4em,left=4mm]{stronghold}\n"
"    \\item Spells from a \\pagelink{Spell Scroll Cards}{Spell Scroll card} can be \\pagetarget{selling Spell Scrolls}{sold for 2~\\svg{gold} each}.\n"
"      Remove sold Spells from the game.\n"
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"除上述内容外，玩家在同一次访问期间可以不限次数地执行以下免费行动：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item 在\\textbf{合作剧本}中：可以将资源给予其他玩家。\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}[before skip balanced=0.4em,left=4mm]{stronghold}\n"
"    \\item 可以将\\pagelink{Spell Scroll Cards}{法术卷轴牌}中的法术\\pagetarget{selling Spell Scrolls}{以每个2~\\svg{gold}的价格出售}。%\n"
"      将出售的法术移出游戏。\n"
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/trading.tex:36
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Other Trading actions}\n"
"Certain game modes and game effects also allow you to trade:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item In \\textbf{Alliance Scenarios}, allies may trade Resources freely at any time on their Turns except during Combat.\n"
"  \\item In \\textbf{Alliance and Cooperative Scenarios}, allies may trade \\textbf{Spell} and \\textbf{Artifact} cards in any mix if they have Heroes on adjacent Fields.\n"
"    Only \\textbf{cards from their hands} may be traded and you must give and receive an equal number of cards.\n"
"  \\item When other game effects allow you to \\textbf{trade Resources} (e.g., \\wikilink{events/marketplace}{Marketplace Event}), use the \\hyperlink{Trade Table}{trade table} as well.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\medskip\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{其他交易行动}\n"
"某些游戏模式和游戏效果也允许你进行交易：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item 在\\textbf{同盟剧本}中，盟友可以在其回合的任何时候自由交易资源，战斗期间除外。\n"
"  \\item 在\\textbf{同盟和合作剧本}中，如果盟友的英雄位于相邻格上，则可以任意组合交易\\textbf{法术}和\\textbf{神器}牌。%\n"
"    只能交易\\textbf{其手牌中的牌}，且你必须给出和接收相同数量的牌。\n"
"  \\item 当其他游戏效果允许你\\textbf{交易资源}时（例如\\wikilink{events/marketplace}{市场事件}），也使用\\hyperlink{Trade Table}{交易表}。\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\medskip\n"
"\n"

